'''阿比'''（{{lang-en|Arby's}}）是美國一家三明治連鎖[[快餐店|快餐店]]，擁有3,300多家餐廳，業界收入排名第三<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qsrmagazine.com/reports/qsr50-2013-sandwich-segment-breakdown? |title=The QSR 50 Sandwich Segment |date=August 2013 |first=Sam |last=Oches |work=QSR Magazine |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811153307/http://www.qsrmagazine.com/reports/qsr50-2013-sandwich-segment-breakdown |archive-date=2013-08-11 |access-date=2016-03-09 |publisher=Journalistic Inc.|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2017年10月，《{{le|美食與美酒|Food & Wine}}》雜誌將阿比評為「美國第二大三明治連鎖店（僅次於[[赛百味|Subway]]）」。<ref name="fw-2017oct18">{{cite news |url=http://www.foodandwine.com/news/arby-deep-fried-turkey-sandwich |title=Deep Fried Turkey Sandwiches Have Arrived at Arby's |work=Food & Wine |date=2017-10-18 |first=Mike |last=Pomranz |accessdate=2021-01-03 |archive-date=2019-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110171221/https://www.foodandwine.com/news/arby-deep-fried-turkey-sandwich |dead-url=no }}</ref>

阿比由{{le|Inspire Brands|Inspire Brands}}持有，Inspire Brands已更名為Arby's Restaurant Group，Inc.（ARG）。隨著公司於2018年2月5日接管[[布法罗狂野鸡翅|水牛城狂野雞翅]]的所有權，ARG被更名。<ref name=nrn>{{cite news|last1=Thorn|first1=Bret|title=Arby's, Buffalo Wild Wings new parent Inspire Brands debuts|url=http://www.nrn.com/mergers-acquisitions/arby-s-buffalo-wild-wings-new-parent-inspire-brands-debuts|access-date=2018-02-07|work=Nation's Restaurant News|date=2018-02-05|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006223546/https://www.nrn.com/mergers-acquisitions/arby-s-buffalo-wild-wings-new-parent-inspire-brands-debuts/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ap>{{cite news|title=Arby's closes deal for Buffalo Wild Wings, makes new company|url=http://www.startribune.com/arby-s-closes-deal-for-buffalo-wild-wings-makes-new-company/472765433/|access-date=2018-02-07|work=Star Tribune|agency=Associated Press|date=2018-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207122301/http://www.startribune.com/arby-s-closes-deal-for-buffalo-wild-wings-makes-new-company/472765433/|archive-date=2018-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

除了招牌的烤牛肉和切達干酪牛肉三明治之外，阿比的產品還包括熟食風格的Market Fresh三明治系列、希臘旋转烤肉、炸薯條和Jamocha奶昔。<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite press release |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/arbys-foundation-invests-3-million-in-the-fight-to-end-childhood-hunger-in-georgia-186340312.html |title=Arby's Foundation Invests $3 Million in the Fight To End Childhood Hunger in Georgia |publisher=The Arby's Foundation |date=2013-01-10 |website=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]] |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |access-date=2021-01-03 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124133619/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/arbys-foundation-invests-3-million-in-the-fight-to-end-childhood-hunger-in-georgia-186340312.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>它的總部位於[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[桑迪斯普林斯_(佐治亚州)|桑迪斯普林斯]]，是[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]的郊區，並使用亞特蘭大的通訊地址。截至2019年，阿比共有3,472間餐廳<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.entrepreneur.com/franchises/arbys/282098|title=Arby's Franchise Information|website=Entrepreneur|language=en|access-date=2019-06-13|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104004801/https://www.entrepreneur.com/franchises/arbys/282098|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美國以外的六個國家及地區設有地點：加拿大、土耳其、卡達、科威特、埃及和韓國。

曾以「雅比」為名於1980年代中期引進台灣，不久後撤出。

